===Noun===
'''fluke'''
# a lucky or improbable occurrence, with the implication that the occurrence could not be repeated: The first goal was just a fluke.
# either of the two lobes of a whale's tail
# any of the triangular blades at the end of an anchor, designed to catch the ground
# a [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trematode trematode]: parasitic flatworm of the trematoda class, related to the tapeworm .

